---
---

<!-- Section 3: How it works, 3 steps (CRO: removes uncertainty) -->
<section class="section section--tint con-steps">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="con-steps__head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Simple &amp; Stress-Free</p>
      <h2 class="con-steps__heading">How Your Consultation Works</h2>
    </div>

    <ol class="con-steps__list">

      <li class="con-steps__step">
        <span class="con-steps__num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <h3 class="con-steps__step-title">Request Your Visit</h3>
        <p class="con-steps__step-body">
          Fill out the quick form below or give us a call. We&rsquo;ll reach out within 24 hours to
          find a time that works for you.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="con-steps__step">
        <span class="con-steps__num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <h3 class="con-steps__step-title">Personalized Skin Assessment</h3>
        <p class="con-steps__step-body">
          Our team takes a close look at your skin type, concerns, and goals, and answers every
          question you have along the way.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="con-steps__step">
        <span class="con-steps__num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <h3 class="con-steps__step-title">Your Custom Treatment Plan</h3>
        <p class="con-steps__step-body">
          You leave with a clear, tailored roadmap of the treatments that will get you the results
          you&rsquo;re after, at a pace that fits your life and budget.
        </p>
      </li>

    </ol>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .con-steps .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .con-steps__head {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .con-steps__head .eyebrow { margin: 0; color: var(--color-cta); }

  .con-steps__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .con-steps__list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    counter-reset: step;
  }

  .con-steps__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    text-align: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .con-steps__num {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-cta);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .con-steps__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-subheading);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .con-steps__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 320px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .con-steps__list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
